name: ΛI.TΛNGLΞMΞNT
description: Digital mythology is an artistic genre created by Lumi co-opting archetypal stories, iconography, and imagery to lead viewers down a path of exploration asking what it means to be a member of mankind in an age where the rapid development of technology reveals the fundamental absurdity of human existence. Featuring prominent themes of futurism, spirituality, and consciousness, digital mythology combines the oldest existential human stories with the heights of futuristic technology in a stark display of dystopic splendor.
